ions. This move aims to reduce delays and prevent fraudulent practices.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/important-update-for-lda-allottees-download-your-allotment-letters-online-now/129914994?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-43054/129914994.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}]}